						<summary>

						<p>On a slab set up in front of the Siddhēśvara temple in the village.</p>						

						<p>Records the gift of a village Tēṟāla to the temple of Siddhēśvara by Mahāmaṇḍalēśvara Mallidēvarāja. The above gift was entrusted to Mallikajiyya.</p>						

